# Microsoft Office temp lock files
~$*

# Secrets — never commit. We sometimes drop credential downloads in the
# repo dir while wiring a service. Anyone with these can impersonate
# Amoura against the corresponding provider.
#   - Firebase service account JSON (FCM push, OneSignal Android setup)
#   - Apple APNs auth key (.p8) for iOS push — also covered by *.p8 above
#   - Generic service-account / private-key downloads
Firebase Key/
firebase-key/
*-service-account*.json
*firebase-adminsdk*.json
AuthKey_*.p8
